sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    actor UR as Unit Representative (User)
    actor G1 as G1/Admin
    actor TM as Team Member
    participant SYS as System (Backend/DB)

    Note over UR,SYS: Phase 1 - Ticket Creation
    UR->>SYS: Create Ticket (Title, Description, Priority)
    SYS-->>UR: Ticket Created (Status: OPEN)

    Note over G1,SYS: Phase 2 - Triage & Allocation
    G1->>SYS: View Open Tickets
    SYS-->>G1: List of Open Tickets
    G1->>SYS: Allocate Ticket to Team (e.g., Electrical)
    SYS-->>G1: Ticket Updated (Status: ALLOCATED)

    Note over TM,SYS: Phase 3 - Resolution
    TM->>SYS: View Allocated Tickets
    SYS-->>TM: List of Allocated Tickets
    TM->>SYS: Add Resolution Notes
    TM->>SYS: Mark Ticket as Resolved
    SYS-->>TM: Ticket Updated (Status: RESOLVED)

    Note over UR,SYS: Phase 4 - Verification & Closure
    UR->>SYS: View Resolved Tickets
    SYS-->>UR: List of Resolved Tickets
    UR->>SYS: Verify Fix

    alt Fix Verified
        UR->>SYS: Close Ticket
        SYS-->>UR: Ticket Updated (Status: CLOSED)
    else Fix Not Verified
        UR->>SYS: Reopen Ticket
        SYS-->>UR: Ticket Updated (Status: OPEN or ALLOCATED)
    end